*Zvao* je prijatelje da dođu na proslavu. (He called his friends to come to the celebration.)

*Zvao* sam čoveka da mi pomogne. (I called a man to help me.)

*Zvao* je policiju da zaštiti svoju imovinu. (He called the police to protect his property.)

On je *zvao* da obavesti da je stigao. (He called to announce that he had arrived.)

*Zvao* je doktora da ga pregleda. (He called the doctor to examine him.)

Ona je *zvala* da traži savet. (She called to ask for advice.)

On je *zvao* da se izvini. (He called to apologize.)

*Zvale* su se devojke da se dogovore za izlazak. (The girls called each other to arrange to go out.)